            <h2 class="blog-post-title">The Hardest Parts of Startups Aren't What You Think</h2>
            <div class="img-responsive">
            <img src="https://unsplash.imgix.net/43/9XkFhM8tRiuHXZRCKSdm_ny-2.jpg?q=75&fm=jpg&auto=format&s=fe6ae3e17cc7d7557206363f26090342">
